# Non-negotiable excludes under sessions/. Commit policy (what to keep vs
# leave out deliberately) lives in sessions/README.md; this file covers only
# the patterns that should never be committed regardless of session outcome.

# Python / notebook ephemera
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Editor / OS cruft
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Secrets — never commit under sessions/
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
.netrc
wandb/

# Large profiler outputs — store externally and link from FINAL_SUMMARY.md.
# Do not commit these formats under any size; small extracts belong in
# artifacts/profiles/ as text or JSON summaries instead.
*.qdrep
*.nsys-rep
*.ncu-rep
*.prof
*.pb
*.sqlite
*.sqlite-journal
